on/Knowledge/.git/index\n---renderer---\nbody.ts  3.6K\ndedup.ts  4.3K\nid.ts  1.7K\nindex-md.ts  2.8K\npaths.ts  1.2K\nregistry.ts  4.6K\nrender.ts  4.6K\nstore.ts  13.2K\n---\nsrc/artifacts/body.ts:7: * rendered by the CLI from fields. `--body` input may only supply authored\nsrc/artifacts/body.ts:66:        `body section \"## ${part.heading}\" is machine-owned and rendered by the CLI — remove it from --body`,\nsrc/artifacts/render.ts:6:export function renderArtifact(\nsrc/artifacts/render.ts:13:  // into a rendered artifact they execute on file creation and prompt the user.\nsrc/artifacts/render.ts:16:  const withLists = renderEachBlocks(stripped, values);\nsrc/artifacts/render.ts:58: * per list item with `{{this}}` substituted; the else branch renders when the\nsrc/artifacts/render.ts:62:function renderEachBlocks(body: string, values: NormalizedRecord): string {\nsrc/artifacts/store.ts:12:import { applyDefaults, orderBySchema, renderArtifact } from \"./render\";\nsrc/artifacts/store.ts:173:    const content = renderArtifact(template, orderBySchema(schema, result.value), bodySections);","stderr":"","interrupted":false,"isImage":false,"noOutputExpected":false}}
